OL,3,CMark Addy to join Guernsey-based film
OL,5,FActor Mark Addy will join the cast of
OL,6,FSwap, a film that will be shot
OL,7,Fentirely in Guernsey.
OL,9,FThe 62-year-old has previously starred
OL,10,Fin a range of hit television shows and
OL,11,Fmovies, including King Robert
OL,12,FBaratheon in A Game of Thrones, DC
OL,13,FGary Boyle in The Thin Blue Line, and
OL,14,FDave Horsefall in The Full Monty.
OL,16,FFilming for his latest project will
OL,17,Fbegin at the end of June, with a cast
OL,18,Fthat also includes James Howard, Sarah
OL,19,FSimpkins and Dean Hollingsworth.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
