OL,3,CMark Addy to join Guernsey-based film
OL,5,FThe plot of Swap will focus on the
OL,6,Fstory of a painter named Jo.
OL,8,FLocal production firm Ivy Gate Films
OL,9,Fsays the character will "confront her
OL,10,Fpast and see it upset her present
OL,11,Flife".
OL,13,FFrances Le Tissier from the company
OL,14,Fsays: "We are looking forward to
OL,15,Fbringing some of Guernsey's wonderful
OL,16,Fscenery to the screen and show it to
OL,17,Fthe rest of the world in a modern
OL,18,Fstory and setting."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
