OL,3,CMark Addy to join Guernsey-based film
OL,5,FThe island has featured on the big
OL,6,Fscreen before, most notably in The
OL,7,FGuernsey Literary and Potato Peel Pie
OL,8,FSociety.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, across the water, the
OL,11,Freturn of the Jersey detective series
OL,12,FBergerac has attracted attention to
OL,13,Fthe Channel Islands.
OL,15,FHowever, both of those productions saw
OL,16,Fconcerns raised about the amount of
OL,17,Ffilming done in the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
