OL,3,CMark Addy to join Guernsey-based film
OL,5,FIn the case of Bergerac, TV executives
OL,6,Fsaid they hoped that viewers would
OL,7,Fspot more local locations as the
OL,8,Freimagined show returned for a second
OL,9,Fseries earlier this year.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Jersey-born actor James
OL,12,FWilkinson is starring in the new
OL,13,FHollywood film Masters of the Universe
OL,14,Falongside Idris Elba. He recently
OL,15,Fannounced plans for a short film shot
OL,16,Fentirely in Jersey.
OL,18,FSwap will be directed by Andrew T
OL,19,FHislop, best known for his work on
OL,20,FLast Flamingo of the Red Summer Sunset
OL,21,Fand Indulgence.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
