OL,3,CMark Addy to join Guernsey-based film
OL,5,FIt is expected to be released in early
OL,6,Fsummer 2027 and the producers have
OL,7,Fsaid they "are planning on as little
OL,8,Fdisruption as possible", but have
OL,9,Fasked Guernsey residents to "please
OL,10,Fbear with us if we are filming in
OL,11,Fpublic areas".
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel breaks down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
